{"tid":42121,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[LIHKG 首發] Omnicharge Pro 20400Mah 尿袋 review","createTime":"2016-12-16T12:10:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T14:52:09.000Z","uid":1826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a76bd6c92d51c800cc1120f5482f1ffe06f7098","tid":42121,"uid":1826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"無估計錯既話, 應該係香港第1個人出既review.  Omnicharge <span style=\"color: red;\">只係得網上有得買</span>, 佢最大既特點, 係個charger 有電插位, 即係你攞屋企把風扇出街, 再插落去都用到.  亦所以所有電話, 包括 Laptop/Macbook 都差到電.<br />\n<br />\n 我其實本來係買左隻Standard 13600Mah 既版本, 不過因為趕住聽日旅行, 佢地搵左隻Pro 版俾我頂住先.  Pro 版係大隻d, 不過就有20400Mah.  一個電插socket, 同有Wireless charging , 一個DC output 俾電器既Adapter 插, 仲會support QC 3.0.   Standard 版就咁有2個 2.4A 既USB port, 同一個電插socket.  我個人覺得有電插socket 都唔洗要DC output 個窿.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img922/6889/3BUizi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg922%2F6889%2F3BUizi.jpg&h=476a86e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPro  版既 Size 係2隻 Apple 既wireless mouse 咁大到.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img923/7407/MOG1E9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg923%2F7407%2FMOG1E9.jpg&h=e06dd285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隻尿袋仲有個LED screen,  話你聽淨幾多電, 舊電壽命, 現時用緊幾多電, 溫度等等.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img924/7352/kaU69X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg924%2F7352%2FkaU69X.jpg&h=946e0199&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係個插電socket.  佢有2款, 110V 美式, 同220V 歐式.  香港理論上要220v.  不過歐式插頭好難攪, 所以我要左美式.  香港大部份買到既電器, 都有110-220 火牛, 所以我要左較大路既美式.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img924/8283/qLaqz1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg924%2F8283%2FqLaqz1.jpg&h=91ae4dfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19638604d28c0954ad9b1041266c962079ac9b20","tid":42121,"uid":1826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:12:10.000Z","msg":"因為執緊行李無乜點攪佢, 係咁二試左陣, QC 3.0 port 係堅既.  個電插亦真係插部macbook 落去係差到電.<br />\n<br />\n我諗我去完旅行番黎, 會send 番去換番隻standard 版, 因為對我黎講20400Mah 係太大隻, 會換番隻standard 版唔洗攞住咁大舊野."},{"pid":"81ca879351b7c28d03738897f775ae8db0251d00","tid":42121,"uid":24201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:15:44.000Z","msg":"how much?"},{"pid":"e52efe23f52285a69b0751eb8e258aa02317d088","tid":42121,"uid":1826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:11:15.000Z","msg":"Standard 版 $129 USD<br />\n<br />\nPro 版 $199 USD"},{"pid":"8b89808bba7753aab0cae8c7ab56f5cc17a0df52","tid":42121,"uid":264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Standard 版 $129 USD<br />\n<br />\nPro 版 $199 USD</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇長x闊x高 size?"},{"pid":"8b17425e6fa59cc36e52121524513821e6928b17","tid":42121,"uid":1826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:34:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Standard 版 $129 USD<br />\n<br />\nPro 版 $199 USD</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇長x闊x高 size?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img922/3631/KS5Dfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg922%2F3631%2FKS5Dfa.jpg&h=73ca4259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左邊 Standard,  右邊Pro"},{"pid":"da25b2e5b772abc8474664dbf8fc113bf42e231c","tid":42121,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:34:26.000Z","msg":"磚頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a274fd335d9660a5bc3cf97f382cbae644c17c64","tid":42121,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:01:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3418beb90ec6db0f8ab34b0a9b4fb4ab5ee1f04f","tid":42121,"uid":60700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:43:08.000Z","msg":"好大舊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b172c4d815d587034983b39d21e174f63fb6eb","tid":42121,"uid":3967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:50:21.000Z","msg":"上到飛機咩？"},{"pid":"df876fc6a2c5ee2ec7631894d39d3ee0d2da1625","tid":42121,"uid":1826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:52:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上到飛機咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢網頁個FAQ 有講.  係無問題.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Can I take Omnicharge on an airplane?</strong><br />\n<br />\nBoth Omnicharge Pro and Standard can be with you in your carry-on luggage. The capacity of Omnicharge Standard (13600mAh/49Wh Max Output 65W) and Omnicharge Pro (20400mAh/73Wh Max Output 100W) falls within Federal Aviation Administration&rsquo;s safety limit of 100Wh.<br />\nPlease click this link for more detailed information:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.faa.gov/about/initiatives/hazmat_safety/more_info/?hazmat=7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faa.gov%2Fabout%2Finitiatives%2Fhazmat_safety%2Fmore_info%2F%3Fhazmat%3D7&d=eWIWh0ev6rHAwRz%2FCIq26ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=5e27b8c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.faa.gov/about/initiatives/hazmat_safety/more_info/?hazmat=7</a>"}]}